1022:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function does the same as CapSense_1_CSDSetupWidget() and also
1023:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  does the following tasks:
1024:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    1. Connects the first sensor of the widget.
1025:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    2. Configures the IDAC value.
1026:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    3. Initializes an interrupt callback function to initialize a scan of the
