1175:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_1_RunTuner() - (see the CapSense_1_RunTuner() function
1176:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  description for more details), the sensor must be preconfigured again by
