1216:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** ****************************************************************************//**
1217:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
1218:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \brief
1219:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function initiates a scan for the sensors of the widget initialized by the
1220:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_1_CSDSetupWidget() function.
1221:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
1222:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** * \details
1223:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function performs scanning of all the sensors in the widget configured by
1224:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  the CapSense_1_CSDSetupWidget() function. It does the following tasks:
1225:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    1. Connects the first sensor of the widget.
1226:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    2. Configures the IDAC value.
1227:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    3. Initializes the interrupt callback function to initialize a scan of
1228:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *       the next sensors in a widget.
1229:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *    4. Starts scanning for the first sensor in the widget.
1230:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
